  <name>Commons Validator</name>
  <description>
    Commons Validator provides the building blocks for both client side validation and server side data validation.
    It may be used standalone or with a framework like Struts.
    This is a port for GWT, which enables program, to use Apache Commons Validator
    also in the frontend compiled by the gwt compiler to java-script.
  </description>
